{"kind":"article","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Fine-grain configuration of SpaceKit’s internal behaviours can be achieved by providing a configuration file.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Configuration file","anchor":"Configuration-file","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SpaceKit configuration should be provided as a simple JSON file with a dictionary top-level."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It is recommended that the configuration file is added to your app as a bundle resource, by including it in your app’s target."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Example SpaceKit configuration JSON:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["{","\t\"enableTeleport\": true,","\t\"enableLevelSwitcher\": true","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"json"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Using-a-configuration-file-with-SpaceKit","text":"Using a configuration file with SpaceKit"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To apply a configuration file when initialising SpaceKit:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Create a URL reference to the file’s location in your app bundle:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let configuration = Bundle.main.url(forResource: \"spacekitconfiguration\", withExtension: \"json\")"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Initialise SpaceKitContextFactory by passing in the URL:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let context = try await SpaceKitContextFactory(venue: venue, configurationFileURL: configuration).make()"]}]}]},{"anchor":"Example-keys","type":"heading","text":"Example keys","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are some examples of keys that can be used in Sp